    <item>
      <title>Meta 改进了 Facebook 的 Feed 功能以抵御 TikTok 并赢回年轻用户</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/facebook-pushes-recommendations-to-rival-tiktok-win-back-young-adults</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Facebook 母公司 Meta Platforms Inc. 过去几年一直在对其旗舰社交网络应用程序进行彻底改造，对人们的推送消息进行调整，以提供更广泛的帖子和视频，以抵御来自 TikTok 的竞争并赢回年轻用户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/facebook-pushes-recommendations-to-rival-tiktok-win-back-young-adults</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 16:44:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雷诺将在中国开发大量售价低于 20,000 欧元的电动汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/renault-said-to-develop-sub-20-000-twingo-ev-in-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，雷诺汽车公司 (Renault SA) 将在中国开发大部分售价低于 20,000 欧元（21,700 美元）的 Twingo，此举是该制造商加快将平价电动汽车推向市场的举措之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/renault-said-to-develop-sub-20-000-twingo-ev-in-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 16:20:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊获监管机构批准扩大美国无人机服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/amazon-to-expand-us-drone-service-after-getting-regulator-s-nod</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司的 Prime Air 无人机项目已获得美国监管机构的批准，允许设备在飞行员的视线之外飞行，从而增加飞行范围并让更多客户享受该服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/amazon-to-expand-us-drone-service-after-getting-regulator-s-nod</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 11:52:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
